tsfelder von Christian Brünner in der Form dargestellt, dass zum einen einschlägige Schriften bzw. Dokumente aus seinem Werk abgedruckt werden und zum anderen einschlägige (Fach-)Beiträge von (jüngeren) WissenschafterInnen in Bezug auf Christian Brünners thematische Schwerpunkte präsentiert werden.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 30. Aug 2021) 7aPOLITICAL SCIENCE / General.2bisacsh  aFestschrift Christian Brünner, Politik, Verwaltung.1 aHackl, Elsa, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aHauser, Werner, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aHauser, Werner, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aKmetic, Konrad, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aKraker, Margit, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aKönigsberger, Georg, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aMayer, Hannes, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aNeger, Thomas, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aNoll, Alfred J., econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aPabel, Katharina, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aPirker, Jürgen, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aPlettenbacher, Ulrike, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aRinner, Anita, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aSchnedl, Gerhard, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aSoucek, Alexander, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aThomasser, Andreas, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aThomasser, Andreas, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/r